---
title: "US63 — Manage marketing website"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>WebsiteAdminScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ManageWebsiteContent
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WebsiteContent
  A->>B: open Website tab
  B->>C: loadContent(section)
  C->>E: fetchWebsiteContent(section)
  E-->>C: WebsiteContent (section)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (content)
  A->>B: edit hero / pricing / FAQ / testimonials, tap PUBLISH
  B->>C: save(section, content)
  C->>E: updateWebsiteContent(section, content)
  E-->>C: WebsiteContent (published)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (published)
  B-->>A: marketing site reflects the change
  note over E: fetchWebsiteContent / updateWebsiteContent via SupabaseGateway (RLS admin-only).<br/>content stored in DB, not hardcoded
